and, pure-play software products don=E2=80=99t own the transaction, so they=
 physically can=E2=80=99t be as smooth, accurate, or instant as Ramp.
Ramp exists in a sweet spot: it=E2=80=99s an engineering and product-driven=
 company slash corporate card (and not the other way around [https://email.=
mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUMtqwzAQ_BrraPROfNChUPIHvfRiZGlrq7ElI61i_PdVkkNhYWGG=
